OL,6,FIssues around crime also made the top
OL,7,F10 fears for parents in 2024 for the
OL,8,Ffirst time (24%), significantly up
OL,9,Ffrom 13% last year.
OL,11,FWorries about future pandemics or
OL,12,Fglobal health crises are relatively
OL,13,Flow on the list of concerns for both
OL,14,Fparents (10%) and young people (6%).
