OL,3,CCost of living tops parents' fears for
OL,4,Cchildren's futures ` study
OL,6,FMichelle Pearce-Burke, co-founder of
OL,7,FWealthify, said: "Given the tough
OL,8,Feconomic environment over the past few
OL,9,Fyears, it's not surprising that
OL,10,Fworries about the cost of living
OL,11,Fcontinue to dominate parents' and
OL,12,Fyoung people's outlook.
OL,14,F"Even though we're starting to see a
OL,15,Flight at the end of the tunnel for the
OL,16,Feconomy, the cost of living is still a
OL,17,Fpainful issue around the country and
OL,18,Fmany people are significantly worse
OL,19,Foff than they were a few years ago."
